{"id": "1221400023837970473", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "😘感谢我们程序A的补充。\n总结来说，圣婴战中墨菲展开粉色屏障时出现的文字，就是图鲁的狂气爆【星辰正位之刻】的原文Ph'nglui mglw'nafh Cthulhu，以及墨菲3费技能【螺湮逆流】的li’hee。\n从图鲁语音【闲话·关于关于神之血脉：这女孩身上流淌着的，毫无疑问是余之血脉……不，余的年纪还不足以留下子嗣。但是，她的力量确实与余同宗。】可以看出，墨菲的力量与图鲁同源，所以这大概也就是墨菲可以使用【星辰正位之刻】的力量的原因。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T10:07:38.198000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-24T10:14:26.546000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1221400023347105843", "filename": "Image_1711273992211.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1811496, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1221400023347105843/Image_1711273992211.png?ex=69ccee6a&is=69cb9cea&hm=0d1839fd5d306bbfea11005e38cfdc3d36bfb1c3ba3536eed92a26858ff68ed0&"}, {"id": "1221400023909011537", "filename": "Image_1711273995492.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1118847, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1221400023909011537/Image_1711273995492.png?ex=69ccee6a&is=69cb9cea&hm=3db9d19bc4b6f6df3a80d5739ce527544fc6ad34ab3f89f1c191e102873733b2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221403914553790505", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "值得一提的题外话，解锁图鲁【闲话·关于神之血脉】的条件是有唤醒体墨菲和艾继丝其中之一即可。\n从目前游戏剧情的角度来说，墨菲的能力很好理解。可艾继丝可能就摸不着头脑，毕竟界域都差了一个。\n但是从原型的角度考虑，这就是合理的。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T10:23:05.817000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221404258855948288", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "墨菲的原型是【克希拉】，即克苏鲁的女儿。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T10:24:27.905000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1221404258637713448", "filename": "Image_1711275644312.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 86153, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1221404258637713448/Image_1711275644312.jpg?ex=69ccf25b&is=69cba0db&hm=9cfe22166d17ebbf9a20d06c7eac867d04a59425037cb5a278cbe04c8a45c4fa&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221404414552571914", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "而艾继丝的原型是【加塔诺托亚】，也就是克苏鲁的儿子", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T10:25:05.026000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1221404414116495405", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-03-24-18-18-41-46_439a3fec0400f8974d35eed09a31f914.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 599484, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1221404414116495405/Screenshot_2024-03-24-18-18-41-46_439a3fec0400f8974d35eed09a31f914.jpg?ex=69ccf280&is=69cba100&hm=761b7bd97a50f326eeebe5ce834eee95578afd8ad85ca527d885a4af0bb82cda&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221405808516927529", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "也就是为什么可以拥有其一唤醒体就能解锁的语音的背后故事（？）\n具体原文以及详细考据就不扩展了，毕竟重点还是研究自造语。\n\n介于唤醒体的战斗技能会有文字特效，之后大概会研究一下深海系怪物（比如永恒助祭等）释放技能时会不会出现文字，希望有收获。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T10:30:37.373000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221488048802631680", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "🎉 🎉 🎉\n今天告诉大家一个好消息，利莫里亚语已经全部补充完毕了，文字已经在制作中，做好了以后会发在同人区供大家欣赏~\n\n然后我们继续补充一下，剩下的还没有提到的几个在哪里出现。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T15:57:24.985000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221488510347902987", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "我们亲爱的程序A找到了造物上出现的利莫里亚文字，请记住他——意识铭刻！", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T15:59:15.026000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1221488510146707608", "filename": "Image_1711295092905.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 299279, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1221488510146707608/Image_1711295092905.png?ex=69cc9812&is=69cb4692&hm=77e4732630b77bce04d733cdc3b64876b241e59a1372cb19c1584c38b3739c50&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221490041931698217", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "这里先不管造物介绍说的什么古老部族需要刻利莫里亚文，只管能看到什么。\n结合之前已经有的文字，可以定位到这就是按26字母表顺序排列的、5个字母一行的表格。\n从最清晰的地方，也就是最下面一行开始看，可以得到v w x y z（新获得x y z）", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T16:05:20.184000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-24T16:06:30.973000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221490808650338314", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T16:08:22.984000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1221490808385962096", "filename": "Image_1711296473157.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 4824, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1221490808385962096/Image_1711296473157.jpg?ex=69cc9a36&is=69cb48b6&hm=a8cf1664a79e2cdf5e7747952ab8b89770d264ab0a307920e7a3238e4babb6a8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221491311736262717", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "倒数第二行则是：\nq r s t u（新获得q）\n但是很显然这太糊了！并不能算是有效信息，顶多能看到一个大概轮廓。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T16:10:22.929000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1221491311555641456", "filename": "Image_1711296582889.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 8395, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1221491311555641456/Image_1711296582889.png?ex=69cc9aae&is=69cb492e&hm=eb924aed97addceaff287a81755b942a1706991a76f12ee1274f783b3453d86c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221492221476606023", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "倒数第三行：\nl m n o p\n全部是已知信息。\n\n倒数第四行，也就是能看到的正数第一行就是：\ng h i j k（新获得j k）", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T16:13:59.828000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221492553220624546", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T16:15:18.922000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1221492553116029078", "filename": "Image_1711296883098.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 14700, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1221492553116029078/Image_1711296883098.png?ex=69cc9bd6&is=69cb4a56&hm=262590482ce0e73b3a515a851c839ea79c50aa83fbb88d293377b2016921acc1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221493293343309847", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "是的，现在我们有了除了B以外的所有字母，而剩下的是我找遍了造物、物资，最终在命轮卡面上看到了最后的内容，也就是——苦咒缚。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T16:18:15.381000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1221493759922147328", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "经过我们的推测与排除，对上了最后的文字，关于阿尔比诺的这张命轮很好的提供了看不清的几个字母。\n\n但遗憾的是，我们怎么都看不懂苦咒缚上写的内容是什么，我们甚至不知道这段文字究竟该怎么排序才能理解。\n这里推测了苦咒缚、阿尔比诺以及蛇神的英文对应拉莱耶语翻译，以及关于阿尔比诺原型相关内容都对不上（蛇神伊格Yig、其女艾伊格Ayi’ig和其子沃尔蒂伊格Voltiyig）。\n希望有能力的守密人可以尝试解决这个难题T T\n\n最后让我们感谢~~头盖骨~~意识铭刻，感谢苦咒缚🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T16:20:06.622000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-24T16:36:57.331000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1221493759720685718", "filename": "Image_1711297126438.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 790100, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1221493759720685718/Image_1711297126438.png?ex=69cc9cf6&is=69cb4b76&hm=3af2a17fd5397b5b52562b56e6288ea04bee0b190d89e19c729f4a299b38f41c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
